{"tid":1459072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"散水撚真係好煩，如果機場和理非都俾人武力清場，你之後仲可以散去邊？","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T23:37:47.000Z","uid":73429,"like":39,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"271d5ee4b71596242fd249183006e0858c4cbb59","tid":1459072,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"真係好撚憎啲on9今日機場和理非都叫人散水，屌你老未以後唔使出啦，遊行都會係陷阱、都會有內鬼。<br />\n如果係街頭遊擊我絕對唔反對散水，絕對要散，因為除左打狗鬧狗，根本無實質影響。<br />\n機場唔同，你坐到多一日，就多一日影響。政府始終要面對。<br />\n重點係，用武力既話無論咩場合唔散水都會有犧牲，咩場合都要散水啦，我屌你老母！<br />\n到時候你會話叫咗一早散？<br />\n和理非集會都武力清場，你仲想散去邊？<br />\n我搵唔到一個地方你班散水撚唔會叫人散"},{"pid":"f37e1c8e3e0a51ba5bb55c322d5ab368d0ad415a","tid":1459072,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"9ba9164cfdad185095d9ed5632cb15abd568ad0c","tid":1459072,"uid":73429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"566b0c7ffa4a2d7161ad966e63e0db9326360994","tid":1459072,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9191934da02f5a9a749cf8b50202c516b937afe","tid":1459072,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"0dfbdd08f0963a5d643d6a2661c4560af0312e09","tid":1459072,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"c016c226ba6eb77beb1e51d472d35ccc3051cbd0","tid":1459072,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566b0c7ffa4a2d7161ad966e63e0db9326360994","tid":1459072,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"去！"},{"pid":"a77194